ng is bubbling and crust is golden. Allow to cool slightly before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can replace the fresh blueberries with defrosted frozen blueberries in this recipe. If using defrosted blueberries, use the simmering basket to drain any excess liquid before using.","You can replace the pure maple syrup with rice malt syrup in this recipe.","For a decadent dessert, serve warm with Cashew pouring cream (refer to the recipe on this recipe chip)."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 15m","12 slices"]}